data.description: Motivated Seller! Seller has decluttered please see new photos!  Welcome to Windermere Estates, where this like new home is ready for its new owners.  Located in a prime Leland, NC area, with quick access to shops, restaurants and medical facilities, and a short drive down to multiple beaches, you'll love it here!  Featuring granite countertops, stainless appliances, with an open concept on the first floor.  A custom deck off the back of the home provides plenty of room for entertainment in the fenced in backyard.  The second floor has an ample owner's suite with walk-in closet is just off the open loft. Loft can be used as office or a 2nd living space.   Two more bedrooms with a full bath await your guest. Schedule a showing today!
